<plot>This promotional short film for the feature _Far from the Madding Crowd (1967)_ (qv) takes us to the many locations in Dorset County, England, where the movie was filmed. It was here that 'Thomas Hardy' (qv) lived and was inspired to write the novel upon which the film is based. Only the film's star, 'Julie Christie (I)' (qv), makes comments on the production.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?340114</url></doc>
